{"tid":845641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邵氏原計畫建影城 他爆因香港迪士尼作罷","createTime":"2018-10-02T23:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T10:15:11.000Z","uid":144018,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"504a950e13eabc76afef0e8e9312021e04c8e60a","tid":845641,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:39:01.000Z","msg":"...//邵逸夫獎基金會主席陳偉文過去在建築師事務所工作，被提拔進邵氏旗下公司，「邵先生天天上班，一坐下，就很有威嚴。」陳當時花3年規畫興建電影城，但計畫因香港迪士尼作罷，他說：「因為迪士尼要進來香港，不希望讓影城和迪士尼互相競爭，就停止這項計畫。」...//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1999060633703896/posts/2275158699427420/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1999060633703896%2Fposts%2F2275158699427420%2F&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1P9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d90c34f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1999060633703896/posts/2275158699427420/</a><br />\n<br />\n究竟一個迪士尼可以打走幾多個主題景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過話就話因為迪士尼啫，話唔定係暗地裡計過條數唔掂咁啱迪士尼又嚟香港，未卸落迪士尼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3034f1b7b71b8edade31c8b50c8d187dc62bcc38","tid":845641,"uid":146435,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/03/074136_7da7165f1366e905d374f443c107b125.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F03%2F074136_7da7165f1366e905d374f443c107b125.png&h=a988f9e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c0ae4d4d36816cd920cef53ca729884a2379a7c","tid":845641,"uid":73092,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T23:41:45.000Z","msg":"邵氏影城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\